comments: Wembanyama (SAS) establishes himself in Exum's (DAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Sochan (SAS) reaches for the ball and marginal contact occurs as he brushes Doncic's (DAL) arm during the steal attempt.
Doncic (DAL) establishes a slightly wide screening position in Jones' (SAS) path and absorbs the majority of the marginal contact to his upper body during the pick.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Replay review of the out of bounds called on Jones (SAS) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Doncic (DAL) touches the ball after the deflection by Jones and is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. Possession is given to the Spurs.
Washington (DAL) brings his arm toward Vassell's (SAS) path and marginal contact occurs at the start of Vassell's drive.
Washington (DAL) jumps alongside Vassell's (SAS) trajectory and avoids contact with his arm during the contest of the driving shot attempt.
Jones (SAS) extends his arm toward the ball and marginal body contact occurs with Exum (DAL) as he spins away on the perimeter.
Doncic (DAL) firms up on his right foot and absorbs the marginal side-to-side contact from Jones (SAS) as Jones goes over the pick.
Wembanyama (SAS) moves laterally into Doncic's (DAL) path and initiates lower body contact that affects Doncic's SQBR during the drive.
At the end of the drive, Doncic (DAL) slightly extends his forearm and marginal contact occurs with Sochan (SAS) as Sochan slips while attempting to come to a stop.
Wembanyama (SAS) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Exum (DAL) initiates illegal contact with Jones' (SAS) back as Jones receives the inbound pass.
A timeout is requested by the Mavericks bench and granted before any contact with Doncic (DAL) on the steal attempt by Sochan (SAS).
Kleber (DAL) shuffles his feet prior to passing.
Johnson (SAS) commits a take foul on Exum (DAL). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Kleber (DAL) brings his arm toward Wembanyama's (SAS) path and marginal contact occurs at the start of Wembanyama's drive.
Irving (DAL) immediately slides his hand off Johnson's (SAS) arm as marginal contact occurs before Johnson's gather and upward shooting motion.
Wembanyama (SAS) cleanly deflects the ball away from Doncic (DAL) on the initial rebound attempt.
